# 📚 Smart Data Display – Trending Books App

This is a simple Flask app that fetches trending books from the Google Books API and displays them as JSON through a /books endpoint.

## 🚀 Features
- Fetches data from Google Books API
- Returns structured JSON: title, description, and link
- Easily extendable for any category

## ⚙ How to Run

### 1. Clone or Download This Project
```bash
git clone https://github.com/tuljayerram/smart-data-display.git
cd smart-data-display

